@startuml
title 基于GitHub的实验管理平台--评定成绩用例的顺序图
actor teachers
== 查看成绩 ==
teachers -> semester: 选择学期
teachers -> course: 选择课程
course -> grades
grades -> tests
tests --> teachers:所选课程的平均成绩
== 评定成绩 ==
teachers -> semester: 选择学期
teachers -> course: 选择课程
teachers -> tests: 选择实验
teachers -> grades : 录入并提交每个实验的成绩
@enduml